{"tid":2249457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒙面法覆核案向泛民索訟費 上訴庭指涉公眾利益拒批政府申請","createTime":"2020-10-19T10:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T10:56:28.000Z","uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2eefcd542fd01f031b081b1a7088d21e5e02eae9","tid":2249457,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"政府早前就緊急法和蒙面法違憲判決上訴得直，其後向興訟的24名泛民議員及梁國雄索取訟費。惟上訴庭今頒判詞指，鑑於本案屬公眾利益案件，下令泛民議員毋須向政府支付訟費。對於政府質疑本案並非對社會整體有利，又指非常多市民支持特首為了止暴制亂所作的事，聲言是「無可爭議的事實」；惟上訴庭指出，特首必須依法行事，此乃法治根本，因此法庭判決特首動用緊急法是否合法，牽涉全港社會利益。<br />\n<br />\n政府和泛民議員之間的訴訟尚未終結，終審法院早前已向雙方批出上訴許可，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">蒙面法聆訊排期於下月24日和25日進行。</span></span>"},{"pid":"74d5efdeefe1864a4c534a3d8f4b107f90bdc4fa","tid":2249457,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/AHISROZN5VDKBN2R54365DYU7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FAHISROZN5VDKBN2R54365DYU7I%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Ztw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=b94d94da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FAHISROZN5VDKBN2R54365DYU7I%2F&h=273ca7ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/AHISROZN5VDKBN2R54365DYU7I/</a>"},{"pid":"367d5ccb494a21db36a7e667ab3e7ecfdaa0e910","tid":2249457,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"【案件編號：CACV541、542、583/19】"},{"pid":"b9d40d05654f95d2910e16b734ffff46c0d11068","tid":2249457,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"個官犯左國安法拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89df13c0798d3dfff1e83a578a5a933e3f98597","tid":2249457,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa